              <Icon name="check" class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mt-1 mr-3 flex-shrink-0" />
              <span class="text-gray-700"><strong>High ceilings</strong> - typically 10-14 feet with period fixtures</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <Icon name="check" class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mt-1 mr-3 flex-shrink-0" />
              <span class="text-gray-700"><strong>Historic windows</strong> - wavy glass, original hardware</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <Icon name="check" class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mt-1 mr-3 flex-shrink-0" />
              <span class="text-gray-700"><strong>Architectural details</strong> - medallions, rosettes, brackets</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <Icon name="check" class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mt-1 mr-3 flex-shrink-0" />
              <span class="text-gray-700"><strong>Period chandeliers</strong> and antique light fixtures</span>
