            <Icon name="paint-roller" class="w-8 h-8 text-white" />
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#333333] mb-3">Plaster Wall Care</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Historic plaster walls are delicate compared to modern drywall. Aggressive scrubbing can damage the surface; harsh chemicals can strip historic paint. We understand proper techniques for cleaning painted plaster without causing harm - maintaining your walls' integrity while removing dirt and grime accumulated over decades.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg border border-gray-200 service-card">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-[#FFA985] to-[#FFC67D] flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <Icon name="crown" class="w-8 h-8 text-white" />
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#333333] mb-3">Period Millwork Detailing</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Your hand-carved mantels, crown moldings, and baseboards define your home's character. We hand-clean these details with appropriate products that won't strip historic finishes or damage aged wood. Every rosette, every bracket, every architectural element receives careful attention - preserving craftsmanship modern homes can't replicate.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg border border-gray-200 service-card">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-[#FFA985] to-[#FFC67D] flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <Icon name="gem" class="w-8 h-8 text-white" />
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#333333] mb-3">Antique & Heirloom Safety</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Many Twickenham homes contain museum-quality antiques, period furnishings, and family treasures passed down through generations. Our team uses lint-free cloths, appropriate products for different materials (wood, brass, silver, marble), and gentle techniques. We never move valuables without permission and communicate about any concerns.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg border border-gray-200 service-card">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-[#FFA985] to-[#FFC67D] flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <Icon name="window-maximize" class="w-8 h-8 text-white" />
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#333333] mb-3">Historic Window Care</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Original wavy glass windows, wood frames, and antique hardware require special attention. We clean historic windows carefully, checking for loose putty or fragile panes before work begins. Your irreplaceable glass is treated with museum-quality care - achieving sparkling clarity without risking damage to 150-year-old materials.</p>
        </div>

