          <p class="text-gray-600">Historic chandeliers, sconces, and fixtures often combine valuable materials with delicate construction. We clean period lighting carefully - understanding which elements can be wiped, which require special products, and when to simply dust. Your antique fixtures maintain their luster without risk of damage or tarnishing.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Services for Historic Homes -->
